<topic id="custom_options">
<title>Custom Options for the AI Positron</title>
<body>
      <p id="p_ag4_3q3_fhc">It is possible to configure certain options for the <b>Oxygen AI
          Positron</b> in the <b>Oxygen XML</b> application.</p>
      <p id="p_rvh_4r3_fhc">The following custom option is supported by adding the option in <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/default-options.html" format="html" scope="external">Oxygen's XML options file</xref>:</p>
      <table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_bg4_3q3_fhc">
        <tgroup cols="3">
          <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="417pt"/>
          <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="70.5pt"/>
          <colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="197.25pt"/>
          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry>Option name</entry>
              <entry>Value</entry>
              <entry>Description</entry>
            </row>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry><i>PLUGIN_CUSTOM_OPTIONS.oxygen.positron.plugin.hide.record.examples.action</i></entry>
              <entry>string</entry>
              <entry>Setting the value to <b>true</b> hides the <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/oxygen-xml-web-author/app/ai_positron_functionality_features.dita#ai_positron_functionality_features/section_a3s_ngn_3fc" format="html" scope="external"><b><u>Record examples for instructions</u></b><u>
                    button</u></xref><u> from appearing in the UI.</u></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
      <p id="p_l2h_qr3_fhc">The following option is supported by <xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/set-parameter-in-startup-script.html#set-parameters-for-application-launchers__setting-a-system-property" format="html" scope="external">setting it as a system property</xref>
        or an environmental variable:<table frame="all" rowsep="1" colsep="1" id="table_r15_bs3_fhc">
          <tgroup cols="3">
            <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="256.5pt"/>
            <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="70.5pt"/>
            <colspec colnum="3" colname="col3" colwidth="360.75pt"/>
            <thead>
              <row>
                <entry>Option name</entry>
                <entry>Value</entry>
                <entry>Description</entry>
              </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <row>
                <entry><i>allow.access.to.ai.positron.service</i></entry>
                <entry>boolean</entry>
                <entry>Setting the value to <b>false</b> hides the possibility
                  to use and configure the <xref href="https://aipositron.oxygenxml.com/" format="html" scope="external">Oxygen AI Positron Service</xref> platform.
                </entry>
              </row>
            </tbody>
          </tgroup>
        </table></p>
    </body>
